CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Bone Biologics Corp is a healthcare solutions provider based in the United States. As a biotechnology firm, it engages its efforts in developing therapeutics to aid bone regeneration. The company's portfolio comprises its lead product, NELL-1, which is a bone void filler. Bone Biologics' technology has application in the surgical specialties of spinal, orthopedic, general orthopedic, plastic reconstruction, neurosurgery, interventional radiology, and sports medicine.
